    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996-generation Carrera offers a visceral, analog driving experience powered by a 3.4L flat-six M96 engine and a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The drivetrain is robust, with the critical IMS bearing and rear main seal recently serviced to ensure long-term reliability. Its chassis features a refined multi-link rear suspension and MacPherson struts, maintaining excellent torsional rigidity and cornering poise. Deceleration is managed by four-piston monoblock calipers for fade-resistant performance. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals are sharp, making this a turn-key example for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
