      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive shape for its mileage. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only the minor road nicks one would expect from careful daily use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with plush seating that shows very little wear; all electronics, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, it is sound\u2014having undergone a recent multi-point inspection and oil service. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, turn-key car that balances luxury with everyday practicality. It\u2019s ready for its next chapter with a driver who appreciates a well-maintained machine.",
