      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust BMW E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to deliver power to the rear wheels via a variable M differential lock. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a full VANOS overhaul, ensuring the chassis remains rigid under high lateral G-loads. The suspension geometry is maintained by refreshed bushings and Bilstein monotube dampers for precise turn-in. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the powertrain remains in peak operating condition, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This is a true driver\u2019s car with excellent mechanical integrity.",
